Hi everyone!

This is a very old match, at one stage I looked like losing it, then my opponent blundered somewhere and I got into a winning position and then I blew it big time and I ended up taking a Low Draw.  This match starts off as a Philidor with a double king pawn opening, me playing 2. Nf3 and black (Daniel) responding with d6.
